   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>To reproduce:

* Click the log in / signup link <a href="http://openhatch.org/account/login/">http://openhatch.org/account/login/</a> on the homepage.
* Click the Yahoo OpenID option. You are taken to <a href="https://login.yahoo.com/config/login?">https://login.yahoo.com/config/login?</a> with a 
long query string.
* Log in to your Yahoo account. You are taken to <a href="http://openhatch.org/openid/register/?next=%2F,">http://openhatch.org/openid/register/?next=%2F,</a> 
where you are not logged in and are asked to pick a hip username.</pre>
